                    <li class="bg-purple-800 text-white  mx-1 py-1 px-1  font-bold w-24 text-center h-full hover:transition hover:bg-white hover:font-bold hover:text-purple-900"><a href="/contact"><i class="fa-solid fa-id-badge"></i> Contact</a></li>
